pageContext.Name: Pink printed georgette saree with blouse
pageContext.Description: Sutram Designer Pink Coloured Silk Georgette Printed Saree. This beautiful casual saree is elegantly decorated with gorgeous prints and pattern that gives a perfect look to the outfit. This saree is an ideal for casual functions and social gathering. Saree comes along with matching fabric unstitched blouse piece. Saree Length : 5.5 mtr, Fabric: Silk Georgette, Blouse Length : 0.80 mtr.
